00:32:10.070 --> 00:32:14.419
permission and everything to authenticate
third parties and let consumers turn on and

00:32:14.419 --> 00:32:16.369
off different third party apps.

00:32:16.369 --> 00:32:21.760
Some of the examples that we have top of mind
